     for CREATE [METHOD POST]
        Request URl=/api(?name&surname&username)
        example /api?name=Hayk&surname=Vardanyan&usernamehvardanyan
        Response USERNAME and USERID   (save your USERID)



     for READ [METHOD GET]
          Request URl=/api/[your USERID]
          example /api/820_ddb5121d-b3b3-46f5-bc7b-90ccd7dc33a
          Request URl=/api/[your USERID]/[json or xml]
          example /api/820_ddb5121d-b3b3-46f5-bc7b-90ccd7dc33a/json
          Response xml/json data



     for UPDATE [METHOD PUT]
          Request URl=/api/[your USERID](?name&surname&username)
          example /api/820_ddb5121d-b3b3-46f5-bc7b-90ccd7dc33a?name=Tigran
          Request URl=/api/[your USERID]/[json or xml](?name&surname&username)
          example /api/820_ddb5121d-b3b3-46f5-bc7b-90ccd7dc33a/json?name=Tigran
          Response xml/json updated data



     for DELETE [METHOD DELETE]
          Request URl=/api/[your USERID]
          example /api/820_ddb5121d-b3b3-46f5-bc7b-90ccd7dc33a
          Response text